{"tid":709243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係泛民】","createTime":"2018-06-20T00:19:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T16:58:30.000Z","uid":27388,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9f06b58d2ae1874ffc95e727d2245b5b9e6b1678","tid":709243,"uid":27388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:19:35.000Z","msg":"泛民5人缺席 港人17億埋單起元朗天橋<br />\n<br />\n//政府計劃係元朗明渠上起一條造價逾17億「架空行人通道」。 起天橋過程仲需要砍37棵樹。  <br />\n<br />\n好多人會話又貴又唔實用，點解政府仲可以起到㗎呢可？ 呢層當然要歸功香港「最堅實反對派」飯民煮派啦。  <br />\n<br />\n議案係上個月 (5月26日) 係立法會工務小組以16票「贊成」，13票「反對」通過。  <br />\n<br />\n望多兩眼，有5名最成日話係「香港最黑暗嘅日子」泛民消失咗。 13+5咪即係18票？ 即係如果呢5名議員郁下佢隻手，都可以力挽狂瀾。 <br />\n___________________________________<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/20/081858_b381b8f5c5bc4789197c7b4100276909.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F20%2F081858_b381b8f5c5bc4789197c7b4100276909.png&h=3ef08c5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戲子唔做戲，仲有咩用？<br />\n<br />\n轉貼"},{"pid":"b3ffa9c9b1ed82a0900064636e17ab6c3de67de2","tid":709243,"uid":38904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:21:19.000Z","msg":"犯民=建制 b 隊"},{"pid":"a53a20bf061653bacfa418f27911453a94c8d5bb","tid":709243,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:21:58.000Z","msg":"區諾軒：要去日本旅行, 區議會投票? 不了！"},{"pid":"8c91eb2e32cca1a89acc5e9f5538b6ff1a0cd7a1","tid":709243,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T00:40:17.000Z","msg":"仲有樓主呢啲有心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfccf6a37956038f7420d5a6ebae46bd4f0bbd16","tid":709243,"uid":62646,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-20T01:00:26.000Z","msg":"泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f429a4861c21dbc70ce203c098783961366b4f","tid":709243,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06